Qalaam — License Allocation
============================

Per ADR-0011 (Docs/adrs/ADR-0011-licensing.md), Qalaam uses a mixed-license
allocation across the monorepo:

  - packages/*                     → Apache License 2.0
  - integrations/homeassistant/    → Apache License 2.0
  - apps/*                         → GNU Affero General Public License v3.0
  - services/*                     → GNU Affero General Public License v3.0
  - tooling/*                      → Apache License 2.0
  - ml/                            → Apache License 2.0 (code); model weights
                                     distributed per upstream weight licenses

Each package's own LICENSE file is authoritative. The root LICENSE files
LICENSE-APACHE-2.0 and LICENSE-AGPL-3.0 contain the full text of each license.

Copyright (c) 2026 Qalaam Maintainers
